{"tid":1170650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為危機】被WiFi聯盟拒門外 美國制裁下再遭重挫 華為手機失去未來 WiFi 技術","createTime":"2019-05-25T06:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T08:07:58.000Z","uid":125193,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db2ff662a59f7b597f5b182fe9de83a14240aa12","tid":1170650,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"美國日前宣佈對中國電訊製造商華為的出口禁令，越來越多重要企業紛紛響應。繼制定SD記憶卡標準的SD協會（The SD Association）將華為從該組織的名單上刪除後，無線網絡認證組織Wi-Fi聯盟（Wi-Fi Alliance）表示，基於特朗普政府最近對華為的技術禁令要求，「暫時限制」華為在該組織的參與活動。<br />\n<br />\n美國科技網站CNET說，華為仍然可以使用目前Wi-Fi和SD記憶卡的相關技術，但可能失去了未來參與新標準制訂的決策權。<br />\n<br />\n另外，制訂半導體產品標準的組織JEDEC透露，華為「自願」退出了該組織。JEDEC說，華為5月17日表示，決定中止在JEDEC的成員身份，直到美國政府施加的限制解除為止。<br />\n<br />\n華為在一份聲明中說：「華為重視與全球所有合作夥伴和協會的關係，瞭解他們所處的困境。我們希望這種情況能夠得到解決，並在努力尋找最佳解決方案」。<br />\n<br />\n被排除在行業標準制定組織之外可能為華為的未來發展帶來衝擊。專家表示，華為仍然有能力生產晶元和產品，但由於缺少影響國際標準制定的能力，未來公司的國際競爭力將受挫。"},{"pid":"ad0aea651f0dc8932eae1139f7e3ffa4eb0dcf3c","tid":1170650,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:45:55.000Z","msg":"【華為危機】被WiFi聯盟拒門外 美制裁下再遭重挫<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190525&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59639621\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190525%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59639621&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62AAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a9074380\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190525%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59639621&h=ee0e82f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190525&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59639621</a>"},{"pid":"8408f5b322ea2d3b5c48ab7abd032c5dd156bfc0","tid":1170650,"uid":60524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"未驚過 華為仲有自家上網技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bae4a30e08017191b3cb9d7611b86a118daf363","tid":1170650,"uid":119897,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8408f5b322ea2d3b5c48ab7abd032c5dd156bfc0","tid":1170650,"uid":60524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"未驚過 華為仲有自家上網技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:51:30.000Z","msg":"有5g 仲要wifi?"},{"pid":"a3ee84f5880da9d194346e3c7e29b16861baa938","tid":1170650,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"買屎為送無限5g<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915f1ac2b7717f6c44d6d84b7251e4a802ca55c6","tid":1170650,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"咁咪岩囉可以自主研發  強國玩開鎖國架嘛"},{"pid":"175b88cbbb2e6ef5b76ccc9ecf16dc9c5a023d08","tid":1170650,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"Wifi standard <br />\n<br />\n一個係華為自己定個新standard <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329fbf3d1e32b8a0fa23e4ab45f8726dff6029de","tid":1170650,"uid":52068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"電話線上網大法"},{"pid":"0b769c1a0454d987f35d009c72e508555e27c7ed","tid":1170650,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:54:57.000Z","msg":"固網流動電話大法"},{"pid":"d295fba6309be186bd85a400b35cc584669746f3","tid":1170650,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:07:58.000Z","msg":"華為5G夠做喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}